StarFlier::

In her innocents to the whole war and conflict between the factions, 
she trustingly looked at Perceptor with childlike innocents and 
ingnorence. "OK. I'm willing to learn something new." she said with a 
grin. Her young and bright optics looking at Perceptor as a young 
girl would at a well liked friend and teacher.
